comments: Brunson (NYK) is not in a legal guarding position when he initiates the body contact with Green (DAL), affecting his SQBR.

Green (DAL) initiates contact with Brunson's (NYK) off-arm, affecting his SQBR. The contact occurs prior to Brunson's gather and upward shooting motion and should therefore be assessed as a non-shooting foul.
Hartenstein's (NYK) steps into Irving's (DAL) path and foot to foot contact occurs that affect Irving's SQBR during the drive.
Randle (NYK) establishes his right foot as his pivot foot and steps off his left foot to release the pass.
Jones Jr. (DAL) reaches for the ball to defend the pass and marginal body contact occurs as he Randle (NYK) come together.
DiVincenzo (NYK) and Powell (DAL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.

Randle (NYK) and Powell (DAL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and incidental contact occurs with Powell's face during the rebound. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Randle (NYK) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
DiVincenzo (NYK) briefly brings a forearm toward Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) space and marginal contact occurs as DiVincenzo releases away during the drive.
DiVincenzo (NYK) avoids stepping out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Green (DAL) rests a hand on Anunoby's (NYK) side as he contests the jump shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
DiVincenzo (NYK) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) signals for and is awarded a timeout as DiVincenzo (NYK) and Green (DAL) come together during the inbound.
DiVincenzo (NYK) commits a take foul on Irving (DAL).
Green (DAL) moves laterally in front of Brunson (NYK) and marginal body contact occurs that does not affect his SQBR.
Irving (DAL) and DiVincenzo (NYK) briefly engage and disengage and upon disengaging, incidental foot contact occurs.
DiVincenzo (NYK) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
